<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="be-located-in-on">be located in / on</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>坐落于；位于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>One of the world's largest art galleries, the Louvre, is located in Paris.
作为世界上最大的艺术博物馆之一的卢浮宫坐落在巴黎。</p><footer>外研③ – 1改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Qingdao is an attractive city located on the eastern coast of China. 
青岛是一座迷人的城市，位于中国东部沿海地区。</p><footer>北师大② – 4</footer></div></div>